  "couplingIntensity": "None",
  "description": "Rapid portamento (0.35 — fast but audible) + morphGlide=0.95 (near-maximum). The constant state is metamorphosis. Play staccato: each note spawns a glide before the next one triggers. Play legato: the glide never completes. Neither approach reaches a static destination. The instrument is permanently mid-transform. bodyFreq=55Hz anchors the habitat while the voice churns above it. Even dividers ÷2, ÷4 keep the harmonic world legible inside the motion chaos.",
